snippet.title: Crew | Trailer | Tabu, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Kriti Sanon, Diljit Dosanjh, Kapil Sharma | March 29
snippet.description:
"Crew" is an entertaining and captivating comic adventure! Three ordinary air hostesses from Mumbai embark on a journey to pursue their dreams but find themselves caught up in unexpected misfortunes. 

This comic caper offers a delightful blend of humour, light-heartedness, and humanism, so sit back, and enjoy this entertaining and uplifting adventure!

#CrewTrailer out now
#CrewInCinemasOnMarch29

Produced by Ektaa R Kapoor & Rhea Kapoor

snippet.title: The Future Of Rail Travel In India | India In Motion Ep 1 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App:
https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

From the world's highest railway bridge, the Chenab Bridge, to the cutting-edge tech hub of the Dedicated Freight Corridor, and India's fastest train to date, the Namo Bharat, to the future fastest train of India - The Bullet train, we travel across India to glimpse the future of train travel.

CurlyTales Editor-in-Chief and National Award Travel Creator Kamiya Jani embarked on a journey to witness clean and magnificent stations that are nothing less than an airport terminal. Onboard our train journey, we experience the lavish hospitality of Vande Bharat trains, relish their delectable food, and marvel at the efficiency and velocity of Namo Bharat.

The magnificence of the Chenab Bridge leaves us spellbound, enhancing the beauty of Jammu & Kashmir. Not merely a means of connectivity, this architectural marvel stands as a tourist attraction in its own. 

Watch the full video to witness how the rail travel in India is going through a transformational stage and how the future of rail travel in India will look like.

Let us know your thoughts in comments below

snippet.title: West Bengal CM Mamata Banerjee Injured, Taken To Hospital | Mamata Banerjee Injury Update
snippet.description:
Mamata Banerjee Injury Reason: West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee suffered major injuries to her forehead, the party informed through a post on X.
The All India Trinamool Congress shared photos of Ms Banerjee on a hospital bed with a deep cut in the middle of her forehead and blood on her face. Sources said the Chief Minister suffered a fall at her home and was taken to the SSKM Hospital in Kolkata. Currently, the wound is being stitched.


#mamatabanerjee #tmc #westbengal
